於1995年12月5日，山達基人員打電話給麥克弗森的家人，說她在美利堡「休息和放鬆」之中，死於腦膜炎或血凝結<ref>{{cite news |last=Plunkett |first=John |url=http://www.lisamcpherson.org/mcphtrb2.htm |title=Scientologist's death: A family hunts for answers |publisher=The Tampa Tribune |date=1996-12-22 |accessdate=2007-05-13 |archive-date=2007-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070819194154/http://www.lisamcpherson.org/mcphtrb2.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sptimes.com/TampaBay/111498/Scientology_charged_i.html |title=Tampabay: Scientology charged in member's death |accessdate=2009-02-11 |archive-date=2009-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090313034529/http://www.sptimes.com/TampaBay/111498/Scientology_charged_i.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。翌日「可疑死亡」調查開始，並進行了驗屍。一年後，清水市警署一個網站要求大眾提供麥克弗森的死亡資料，媒體開始猜測<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lisamcpherson.org/mcphtrib.htm |title=Mystery surrounds Scientologist's death |accessdate=2009-02-11 |archive-date=2007-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070419083837/http://www.lisamcpherson.org/mcphtrib.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>她的死亡原因<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lisamcpherson.org/cwdeath.htm |title=Police: Clearwater police needs your help! |accessdate=2009-02-11 |archive-date=2007-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070419045141/http://www.lisamcpherson.org/cwdeath.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

從此約莫在麥克弗森死的週年，在山達基機機構外有定期示威<ref>[http://www.sptimes.com/News/120901/NorthPinellas/Church_loads_up_for_o.shtml Church loads up for one last fight] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sptimes.com/News/120901/NorthPinellas/Church_loads_up_for_o.shtml |date=20090223052950 }}，DEBORAH O'NEIL, St. Petersburg Times, December 1, 2001</ref>。在2008年2月10日，麗莎的生日，有七千人以上，在全世界百多個城市的山達基機構門外抗議<ref name="johncook">{{cite news| last =Cook| first =John| title =Scientology - Cult Friction: After an embarrassing string of high-profile defection and leaked videos, Scientology is under attack from a faceless cabal of online activists. Has America's most controversial religion finally met its match?| work =Radar Online| publisher =Radar Magazine| date =March 17, 2008| url =http://radarmagazine.com/from-the-magazine/2008/03/scientology_anonymous_protests_tom_cruise_01.php| accessdate =2008-03-20| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080324233413/http://www.radarmagazine.com/from-the-magazine/2008/03/scientology_anonymous_protests_tom_cruise_01.php| archivedate =2008-03-24}}</ref><ref name="MoncadaFeb12">{{cite news |author=Carlos Moncada |title=Organizers Tout Scientology Protest, Plan Another |url=http://suncoastpinellas.tbo.com/content/2008/feb/12/organizers-tout-scientology-protest-plan-another/ |work=[http://tbo.com/ TBO.com] |publisher=The Tampa Tribune |date=2008-02-12 |accessdate=2008-02-13 |archive-date=2012-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210160057/http://suncoastpinellas.tbo.com/content/2008/feb/12/organizers-tout-scientology-protest-plan-another/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RamadgeFeb14">{{cite news | author=Andrew Ramadge | title=Scientology protest surge crashes websites | url=http://www.news.com.au/technology/story/0,25642,23212002-5014239,00.html | work=News.com.au | publisher=News Limited | date=2008-02-14 | accessdate=2008-02-14 | archive-date=2009-06-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604052502/http://www.news.com.au/technology/story/0,25642,23212002-5014239,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==驗屍報告==
在1995年12月5日，麥克弗森的驗屍是由助理驗屍官羅伯特·戴維斯進行。戴維斯從未完成驗屍報告，因為他被要求辭職。<ref name="Crow Memo">{{Cite web
| title = Crow Memo
| accessdate = 2009-02-11
| work = xenutv.com
| url = http://www.xenutv.com/lisa/crowdroppings.pdf
| archive-date = 2008-10-10
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081010180351/http://www.xenutv.com/lisa/crowdroppings.pdf
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>他的上司驗屍官瓊·活完成了報告。

該報告確定麗莎·麥克弗森的死因是左肺動脈血栓塞，由“臥床不動和嚴重脫水”造成，死亡的方式為“未定”。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.lisamcpherson.org/coroner.gif | work=LisaMcPherson.org | title=Coroner's Report | accessdate=2009-02-11 | archive-date=2000-08-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20000816155456/http://www.lisamcpherson.org/coroner.gif | dead-url=no }}</ref>該報告還確定了多個血腫（瘀傷），擦傷了的鼻子，和在右下臂略高於手腕處有皮膚損害，符合了被昆蟲或動物所咬的跡象。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.shipbrook.com/jeff/CoS/autopsy.html | title=Lisa McPherson: Coroner's Report transcript | accessdate=2009-02-11 | archive-date=2001-03-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010313001707/http://www.shipbrook.com/jeff/CoS/autopsy.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>
<ref>{{cite web | url=http://whyaretheydead.net/lisa_mcpherson/autopsy/autopsy_03/ | title=Autopsy Photos - Lisa McPherson (Caution: Disturbing photos) | accessdate=2009-02-11 | archive-date=2007-09-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070926224103/http://whyaretheydead.net/lisa_mcpherson/autopsy/autopsy_03/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

1997年1月21日，瓊·活在電視節目“內部版”指出，驗屍報告顯示麥克弗森惡化緩慢，沒有飲用液體5至10天，體重不足，被蟑螂咬，她死之前昏迷了24至48小時。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.whyaretheydead.net/lisa_mcpherson/is-jan.html | work=whyaretheydead.net | title=Inside Edition Transcript | accessdate=2009-02-11 | archive-date=2009-06-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090605222728/http://www.whyaretheydead.net/lisa_mcpherson/is-jan.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

